<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 7" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 7. Male adult (holotype) of Stenochironomus baishanzuensis Song &amp; Qi, sp. nov. A wing B hypopygium in dorsal C hypopygium in ventral view D legs." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1104.81403.figure7" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/693999" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">7A</figureCitation>
